  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549440/extras/33c082043c8cd3c0417018460e7aa0e3.avif?t=1750741189\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549440/extras_big/33c082043c8cd3c0417018460e7aa0e3.avif?t=1750741189 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All new 2D mode with full native Steam Deck support </strong>— Select VR or 2D mode on launch or run the game natively on the Steam Deck or Linux.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gripper's is leaping into VR</strong> — bringing over 40 mind-bending puzzles designed to test your wits and reflexes in a whole new dimension!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you reach the treasure at the end?</strong><br>Each level challenges you to think creatively and make the most of your environment — all in full VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 <strong>Puzzle Highlights:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use blocks to block enemy sightlines and sneak your way through</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn defeated enemies into makeshift rafts to cross water</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master teleportation mechanics to move yourself, blocks, and other objects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect every key to unlock the exit and advance</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All-new VR controls let you zoom in and out for a fresh perspective</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 40 handcrafted puzzles, with more on the way post-launch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimal hand-holding for a rewarding challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quirky, fun story with charming characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by a beloved classic game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free puzzle updates and new modes coming soon</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're a puzzle master or just getting started, <i>Gripper's VR</i> will pull you in with its clever mechanics and imaginative world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549440/extras/026a98c15bf8a070602d0f9fa9830d0b.avif?t=1750741189\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549440/extras_big/026a98c15bf8a070602d0f9fa9830d0b.avif?t=1750741189 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549440/extras/33c082043c8cd3c0417018460e7aa0e3.avif?t=1750741189\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549440/extras_big/33c082043c8cd3c0417018460e7aa0e3.avif?t=1750741189 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All new 2D mode with full native Steam Deck support </strong>— Select VR or 2D mode on launch or run the game natively on the Steam Deck or Linux.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gripper's is leaping into VR</strong> — bringing over 40 mind-bending puzzles designed to test your wits and reflexes in a whole new dimension!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you reach the treasure at the end?</strong><br>Each level challenges you to think creatively and make the most of your environment — all in full VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 <strong>Puzzle Highlights:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use blocks to block enemy sightlines and sneak your way through</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn defeated enemies into makeshift rafts to cross water</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master teleportation mechanics to move yourself, blocks, and other objects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect every key to unlock the exit and advance</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All-new VR controls let you zoom in and out for a fresh perspective</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 40 handcrafted puzzles, with more on the way post-launch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimal hand-holding for a rewarding challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quirky, fun story with charming characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by a beloved classic game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free puzzle updates and new modes coming soon</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're a puzzle master or just getting started, <i>Gripper's VR</i> will pull you in with its clever mechanics and imaginative world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549440/extras/026a98c15bf8a070602d0f9fa9830d0b.avif?t=1750741189\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549440/extras_big/026a98c15bf8a070602d0f9fa9830d0b.avif?t=1750741189 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
